body:
Hi, is it possible to add this or how can it be done. I would like the ability to add a wrapped section around form elements. For example like this:
```
  form do |user|
    tab :profile do
      row do
        col(sm: 6) { text_field :full_name }
        col(sm: 6) { text_field :username }
      end

      row do
        col(sm: 8) { text_field :email }
        col(sm: 4) { select :user_type, ["A", "B", "C"] }
      end

      divider

      section "Contact Information" do # <---- here
        row do
          col(sm: 4) { phone_field :phone }
          col(sm: 4) { phone_field :cell }
          col(sm: 4) { text_field :pager }
        end
        text_field :address_line_1
        text_field :address_line_2
        row do
          col(sm: 8) { text_field :territory_description }
          col(sm: 4) { text_field :postal_code }
        end
      end
    end

```

Thanks

After testing around a bit. I think it would make sense if section basically runs these two commands together:
```
      well do  # <--- this
        h3 "Contact Information" # <--- and this
        row do
          col(sm: 4) { phone_field :phone }
          col(sm: 4) { phone_field :cell }
          col(sm: 4) { text_field :pager }
        end
        text_field :address_line_1
        text_field :address_line_2
        row do
          col(sm: 8) { text_field :territory_description }
          col(sm: 4) { text_field :postal_code }
        end
      end
```
